<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFLegge1964">Legge, Francis (1964) [1914] (reprinted in two volumes bound as one). <i>Forerunners and Rivals of Christianity, From 330 B.C. to 330 A.D.</i>. New York: University Books. LC Catalog 64-24125.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Forerunners+and+Rivals+of+Christianity%2C+From+330+B.C.+to+330+A.D.&amp;rft.aulast=Legge&amp;rft.aufirst=Francis&amp;rft.au=Legge%2C+Francis&amp;rft.date=1964&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=University+Books&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Manichaeism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
