<li><a href="http://www.harvard-yenching.net/xueshu/zhongya/mani/010.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.harvard-yenching.net/xueshu/zhongya/mani/010.htm" rel="nofollow">The Original Chinese Manichaean Scriptures Online: 摩尼教殘經一</a> ("incomplete Sutra one of Manichaeism")&amp; <a href="http://www.harvard-yenching.net/xueshu/zhongya/mani/011.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.harvard-yenching.net/xueshu/zhongya/mani/011.htm" rel="nofollow">摩尼光佛教法儀略</a>("The Mani Bright Buddha teaching plan") &amp; <a href="http://www.harvard-yenching.net/xueshu/zhongya/mani/012.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.harvard-yenching.net/xueshu/zhongya/mani/012.htm" rel="nofollow">下部贊</a>("The Lower part chant") (Chinese).</li>
</ul>
